{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-301-to-400/problem-396-weak-goodstein-sequence","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"project-euler-problems-301-to-400","demoType":null,"title":"Vežba 396: slabi niz Goodsteina","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Za bilo koji pozitivan ceo broj $n$, sekvenca Goodsteina za n \\{g1, g2, g3, \\ldots\\}$ je definisana kao što slijedi:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>$g_1 = n$</li>\n<li>Za $k > 1$, $g_k$ se dobija zapisivanjem $g_{k - 1}$ u bazi $k$, interpretiranjem kao broj u bazi $k+1$, i oduzimanjem 1.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Niz se završava kada je $g_k$ nula.</p>\n<p>Na primer, niz od šest slabih brojeva Goodsteina je $\\{6, 11, 17, 25, \\ldots\\}$:`</p>\n<ul>\n<li>$g_1 = 6$.</li>\n<li>$g_2 = 11$ jer $6 = 110_2$, $110_3 = 12$, i $12 - 1 = 11$.</li>\n<li>$g_3 = 17$ jer $11 = 102_3$, $102_4 = 18$, i $18 - 1 = 17$.</li>\n<li>$g_4 = 25$ jer $17 = 101_4$, $101_5 = 26$, i $26 - 1 = 25$.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>I tako dalje.</p>\n<p>Može se dokazati da svaka slaba Goodstein sekvenca je ograničena/završava.</p>\n<p>Neka je $G(n)$ broj ne-nultih elemenata u sekvenci slabe Goodsteina.</p>\n<p>Može se dokazati da $G(2) = 3$, $G(4) = 21$ na $G(6) = 381$.</p>\n<p>Može se dokazati da Pia $\\sum G(n) = 2517$ za $1 ≤ n &#x3C; 8$.</p>\n<p>Pronađite poslednjih 9 cifara od $\\sum G(n)$ za $1 ≤ n &#x3C; 16$.</p>\n</section>","id":"5900f4f81000cf542c51000b","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Euler","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"project-euler","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":302061,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-301-to-400/problem-396-weak-goodstein-sequence"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function weakGoodsteinSequence() {\n\n  return true;\n}\n\nweakGoodsteinSequence();","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>weakGoodsteinSequence()</code> trebalo bi da vrati <code>173214653</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(weakGoodsteinSequence(), 173214653);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/project-euler/#project-euler-problems-301-to-400","dashedName":"problem-396-weak-goodstein-sequence","certification":"project-euler","disableLoopProtectTests":true,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"project-euler","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"project-euler-problems-301-to-400","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-301-to-400/problem-397-triangle-on-parabola","prevChallengePath":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-301-to-400/problem-395-pythagorean-tree","id":"5900f4f81000cf542c51000b","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":1,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"script","ext":"js","contents":"// solution required","history":["script.js"],"fileKey":"scriptjs"}]}},"id":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-301-to-400/problem-396-weak-goodstein-sequence"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}